    The stolen glasses of Brother William was returned at fourth day-Prime by Severinus.<br /><br />"Severinus finds the stolen lenses, Nicholas brings the new ones, and william, now with six eyes, goes to decipher the manuscript of Venantius." (p.273)<br /><br />:)<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">(less)</a>
  
